Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:52.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fax-0.1}想い出はモノクローム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}色を点けてくれ
